channel.title: Legend scape The best of the best
channel.description:
Ok hello and welcome to my awesome server. Took me ages to code all of it. Now im done with it i will be relesing another server soon. But that will be called a different name so watch out for it!
Commands: Normal players:
::tank (99 mage 99 def 99 range 99hp) ::pure (99 attack 99 str 1 def 99 range 99 mage 1 pray 99 hp rest 99's) ::starter ::train ::jad ::mystats ::barrows ::afk (thanks reaper ;) ::back ::suggest ::pk ::mb ::male ::female ::fightpits ::drags ::drags2 ::anti ::home ::shops ::modinfo ::skills (no firemaking) thanks reaper though ;) ::slayer ::kqueen ::yell ::players ::mypk ::cwars ::char ::pkbox ::edge ::runes ::arrows
Mod commands (includes all of normal players)
::sweet ::modwear ::kick ::master ::dragonweapons ::food ::notedbarrows ::dragonarmour
Admin commands: (includes the rest)
::adminwear ::banuser ::god ::pnpc (npc id) ::npc ::normal ::xrichie ::xteletome ::xteleto ::bank ::barrage ::pickup Owner commands (every single 1)
::ipban ::mantas (useful whilst pk) ::demote ::giveowner ::givemod ::giveadmin ::xteleall
Thats the commands.
More information.
Ancient teleports Based on reapeage scape but to highly modified
Bank booths at edge and train varrock train is non wild brilliant pking no over hitting. Most specs work!
